name: Get Ready for Office
description: In the morning 7:30 am I start my daily office works. First I take bath for fresh myself. Then I take breakfast.

name: Go to Office
description: I start to go office with my honda cb Trigger. I start journey at 8.30 am. Some of time there is huge traffic jam on the road that's why I start journey early from the office starting time

name: Get Ready for Office works
description: when I reach the office then I take some rest and take a cup to tea for the refreshment. Some of time we discution to each  other about the setuation around of us.

name: Communicating to Client
description: Then I start my regular duties. At first I make some phone call to the clients. My duty is collect money to the defolder customers. In the conversion I try to make a payment date of those clients.

name: Physical Meeting
description: When clients do not response in the phone then I go their office for meet them. In the meeting we fixed the payment process and payment time. If they are not able to office then the very next step is go to their home.

name: Relaxation
description: After the office work I go back to home and I high time to make the mind fresh. That's why I go the relaxation place and take some rest. It's about 2-3 hours then I go back in the house.
